**Lovestruck** | Attribute
__Basics__
On the first night the lovestruck player must select a player to become their lover.
Lovestruck players and their lover will share a channel where they can communicate securely.
A Lovestruck player will gain the alignment of their lover in addidtion to their own.

__Formalized__
Inherit: `Cupid`
Starting: Join #Couple
Immediate Night: [Condition: @Selection is not @Self, Temporal: Night 1] {Forced}
  • Target @Selection (Player) 
  • Grant `Lover` to @Target
  • Add @Target to #Coupl
